{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/MachineLearning/2019-05-12-BasicChapter9-1","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Minsu's Dev Log","author":"Minsu Kim","siteUrl":"https://alstn2468.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"alstn2468/alstn2468.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"eMLdEwU"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"89324ef1-a126-563e-83d7-fa4b0b69fdc6","excerpt":"해당 게시물은 Edwith에서 제공하는\n머신러닝과 딥러닝 BASIC을 듣고 요약 정리한 글입니다. Ultimate Dream 생각하는 기계를 만드는 것 사람의 뇌를 공부하기 시작했다.\n사람의 뇌는 복잡하게 구성되어 있지만 단순하게 동작한다.\n어떠한 input이 존재하고 이것의 길이에 \n따라 신호의 양이 달라진다.  \n이 더해진 값이 어떠한 값 이상이 되면 활성화 상태가 결정된다. 이것을 토대로 만들어진 것이 활성화 함수 (Activation Functions)다. Logistic…","html":"<p>해당 게시물은 <a href=\"https://www.edwith.org\">Edwith</a>에서 제공하는<br/>\n<a href=\"https://www.edwith.org/others26/joinLectures/9829\">머신러닝과 딥러닝 BASIC</a>을 듣고 요약 정리한 글입니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"ultimate-dream\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ultimate-dream\" aria-label=\"ultimate dream permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Ultimate Dream</h2>\n<p><strong>생각하는 기계</strong>를 만드는 것<br/></p>\n<p>사람의 뇌를 공부하기 시작했다.<br/>\n사람의 뇌는 <strong>복잡하게 구성</strong>되어 있지만 <strong>단순하게 동작</strong>한다.<br/>\n어떠한 <strong>input</strong>이 존재하고 이것의 <strong>길이</strong>에 <br/>\n따라 신호의 양이 달라진다. <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>∗</mo><mi>w</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\sum{(x * w + b)}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mop op-symbol small-op\" style=\"position:relative;top:0em;\">∑</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">∗</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02691em;\">w</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span> <br/>\n이 더해진 값이 어떠한 값 이상이 되면 <strong>활성화</strong> 상태가 결정된다.<br/></p>\n<p>이것을 토대로 만들어진 것이 <strong>활성화 함수</strong> (<strong>Activation Functions</strong>)다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"logistic-regression-uniuts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#logistic-regression-uniuts\" aria-label=\"logistic regression uniuts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Logistic regression uniuts</h2>\n<h3 id=\"소프트웨어\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%86%8C%ED%94%84%ED%8A%B8%EC%9B%A8%EC%96%B4\" aria-label=\"소프트웨어 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>소프트웨어</h3>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 586px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 96.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"아직 안만듬\" title=\"아직 안만듬\" src=\"/static/31bfa3a889f94467c69ff9eedd650d79/a76f4/1.png\" srcset=\"/static/31bfa3a889f94467c69ff9eedd650d79/8a4e8/1.png 150w,\n/static/31bfa3a889f94467c69ff9eedd650d79/5a46d/1.png 300w,\n/static/31bfa3a889f94467c69ff9eedd650d79/a76f4/1.png 586w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 586px) 100vw, 586px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n<h3 id=\"하드웨어적\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%98%EB%93%9C%EC%9B%A8%EC%96%B4%EC%A0%81\" aria-label=\"하드웨어적 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>하드웨어적</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Perceptron(Frank Rosenblatt, ~1957)</li>\n<li>Adaline/Madaline(Widrow and Hoff, ~1960)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"andor-problem\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#andor-problem\" aria-label=\"andor problem permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>AND/OR Problem</h2>\n<p>기계가 <strong>AND/OR</strong> 문제를 <strong>예측</strong>할 수 있는 것이 중요했다.<br/>\n<strong>Linear</strong>한 모델을 사용해서 <strong>예측이 가능</strong>하다.<br/></p>\n<h2 id=\"xor-problem\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#xor-problem\" aria-label=\"xor problem permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>XOR Problem</h2>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"아직 안만듬\" title=\"아직 안만듬\" src=\"/static/0ae706e9c2fbedf8e556c44ce185325a/0a47e/2.png\" srcset=\"/static/0ae706e9c2fbedf8e556c44ce185325a/8a4e8/2.png 150w,\n/static/0ae706e9c2fbedf8e556c44ce185325a/5a46d/2.png 300w,\n/static/0ae706e9c2fbedf8e556c44ce185325a/0a47e/2.png 600w,\n/static/0ae706e9c2fbedf8e556c44ce185325a/1cfc2/2.png 900w,\n/static/0ae706e9c2fbedf8e556c44ce185325a/00d43/2.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>X1</th>\n<th>X2</th>\n<th>Y</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>XOR</strong> 문제는 <strong>Linear</strong>한 모델로 예측이 <strong>불가능</strong>하다<br/>\n그래프에 어떠한 선을 그어도 결과를 찾을 수 없다.<br/></p>\n<h2 id=\"perceptrons-1969\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#perceptrons-1969\" aria-label=\"perceptrons 1969 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Perceptrons (1969)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Marvain Minsky (Founder of the MIT AI Lab)</li>\n<li>여러개의 신경망을 합친 <strong>MLP</strong>를 사용하면 해결할 수 있다.</li>\n<li>하지만 <strong>Weight</strong>과 <strong>Bias</strong>는 학습시킬 수 없다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"backpropaagation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#backpropaagation\" aria-label=\"backpropaagation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Backpropaagation</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Paul Werbos (1974, 1982)</li>\n<li><strong>Hinton</strong> (1986)</li>\n<li><strong>Weight</strong>과 <strong>Bias</strong>를 조절하는 것이 어려움</li>\n<li>값을 <strong>뒤로 전달</strong>하며 진행시키는 알고리즘</li>\n<li>더 복잡한 형태의 예측 가능</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"convolutional-neural-networks\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#convolutional-neural-networks\" aria-label=\"convolutional neural networks permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Convolutional Neural Networks</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>LeCun (1980)</li>\n<li>고양이의 신경망 세포를 관찰</li>\n<li><strong>일부</strong>의 신경망 세포가 <strong>활성화</strong>되는 것을 확인</li>\n<li>이미지를 잘라서 <strong>나중에 합치는 방법</strong>으로 학습</li>\n<li>문자와 숫자를 인식하는데 <strong>90% 이상</strong> 정확도</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"a-big-problem\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#a-big-problem\" aria-label=\"a big problem permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>A Big Problem</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Backpropaagation</strong>이 몇 개의 Layer에서 잘 동작</li>\n<li><strong>10여개 이상</strong>에서의 Layer에서 학습시킬 경우 <strong>은닉</strong>을<br/>\n할 수록 약해져 앞쪽으로 갈 수록 에러가 잘 전달되지 않음</li>\n<li>새로운 알고리즘의 발견 (<strong>SVM</strong>, <strong>RandomForest</strong>)</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"딥러닝의 시작과 XOR 문제","date":"May 12, 2019","thumbnail":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/MachineLearning/2019-05-12-BasicChapter9-1/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/MachineLearning/2019-05-04-BasicChapter8-4/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"lab:Meet MNIST Dataset","category":"Machine Learning","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/MachineLearning/2019-05-12-BasicChapter9-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Back-propagation 과 2006/2007 ‘딥’의 출현","category":"Machine Learning","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3001444076","3128451518"]}